20a%20holiday%20event%20at%20one.%20Because%20Disney%20World's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-world-best-things-to-do-in-fall-cast-member%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMickey's%20Not%20So%20Scary%20Halloween%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20currently%20out%20of%20our%20budget%20(it%20would%20require%20flights%20to%20Florida%2C%20park%20tickets%2C%20and%20accommodations)%2C%20we%20opted%20to%20visit%20Legoland's%20Brick-or-Treat%20event%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Halloween-themed%20event%20runs%20from%20October%202%20to%20November%202%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20perfect%20way%20for%20my%20three%20kids%20to%20get%20into%20the%20Halloween%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20visited%20the%20park%20on%20a%20Saturday%2C%20and%20the%20crowd%20was%20manageable.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mom%20with%20three%20kids%20at%20Legoland%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f911910be9845f2dc4e45c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Legoland%20New%20York%20park%20was%20pretty%20empty%20when%20the%20author%20visited.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20visited%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flegoland-new-york-resort-hotel-family-review-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELegoland%20New%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20my%20family%20a%20year%20prior.%20We%20decided%20to%20go%20on%20a%20Friday%20when%20the%20kids%20had%20no%20school%2C%20and%20drove%20from%20Maine%20straight%20to%20New%20York%20to%20hit%20the%20park%20early.%20Turned%20out%20that%20New%20York%20state%20also%20had%20that%20day%20off%2C%20and%20the%20park%20was%20packed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20go%20on%20a%20Saturday%20to%20avoid%20school%20time%20off%20and%20hoped%20the%20crowds%20would%20be%20more%20manageable.%20It%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20true.%3C%2Fp