0up%20trick-or-treating%20stations%20during%20its%20Halloween%20Brick-or-Treat%20event.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20Halloween%20decorations%2C%20the%20Legoland%20Brick-or-Treat%20event%20featured%20several%20trick-or-treating%20stations%20throughout%20the%20park.%20They%20are%20only%20open%20during%20the%20afternoon%2C%20from%202%20p.m.%20to%206%20p.m.%2C%20so%20managing%20our%20kids'%20expectations%20from%20early%20on%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20patience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20stations%20opened%2C%20there%20were%20lines%20of%20people%20at%20each%20of%20them%2C%20but%20they%20moved%20fairly%20quickly.%20Each%20of%20my%20kids%20received%20a%20bag%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fhealthy-halloween-treats%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eallergy-friendly%20treats%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20they%20were%20able%20to%20visit%20a%20couple%20more%20stations%20to%20collect%20extra%20candy.%20All%20the%20stations%20are%20located%20in%20the%20lower%20portion%20of%20the%20park%2C%20so%20we%20didn't%20visit%20all%20of%20them%20since%20we%20were%20moving%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction%20to%20avoid%20the%20crowds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20were%20to%20visit%20the%20park%20again%20during%20Brick-or-Treat%2C%20I%20might%20plan%20our%20visit%20differently%20to%20maximize%20the%20amount%20of%20trick-or-treating%20we%20could%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMost%20rides%20were%20pretty%20empty%20and%20had%20no%20lines.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Legoland%20carrousel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f9170ac007ca8c27376e2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20a%20Saturday%20in%20October%2C%20Legoland%20New%20York%20was%20pretty%20empty.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20accustomed