%20to%20loosen%20thoroughly%20stuck-on%20debris%20and%20truly%20sanitize%20your%20floors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Roborock%20F25%20Ultra%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20wet-dry%20vacuums%20with%20the%20option%20for%20steam%20cleaning%2C%20and%20it's%20the%20first%20time%20I've%20truly%20been%20intrigued%20in%20making%20the%20leap%20from%20my%20trusty%20steam%20mop%20to%20a%20vac-mop%20for%20my%20hard%20floors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20try%20it%20out%20in%20my%20own%20home%2C%20and%20I'm%20happy%20to%20report%20that%20my%20floors%20have%20never%20looked%20shinier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237cf7f20-b7c1-48f8-83cd-7033cbff5169%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%20and%20setup%5C%22%3EDesign%20and%20setup%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227b92103d-1c99-4bb5-8b77-7b8bb3130786%5C%22%3EThis%20machine%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20beast%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20never%20welcomed%20a%20vac-mop%20into%20my%20home%20before%2C%20I%20wasn't%20prepared%20for%20the%20Roborock%20F25%20Ultra%20to%20be%20bigger%20and%20heavier%20than%20my%20everyday%20Dyson%20cordless%20vacuum.%20It%20makes%20sense%20when%20you%20think%20about%20it%3B%20this%20essentially%20combines%20several%20cleaning%20devices%20into%20one%2C%20but%20it%20took%20me%20by%20surprise%20just%20how%20large%20and%20heavy%20the%20vac-mop%20is.%20It%20weighs%2012%20pounds%2C%20which%20is%20on%20the%20heavier%20end%20of%20vac-mops%20we've%20tested.%20It's%20about%20the%20dimensions%20of%20a%20standard%20upright%20corded%20vacuum%2C%20but%20is%20entirely%20cordless.%20Instead%2C%20a%20base%20charges%20and%20dries%20the%20mop%20when%20not%20in%20use.%20Due%20to%20its%20large%20size%2C%20the%20vac-mop%20has%20motorized%20wheels%20to%20help%20you%20move%20it%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20a%20place%20to%20store%20this%20behemoth%20in%20my%20tiny%20apartment%20has%20been%20no%20small%20feat.%20It%20currently%20lives%20awkwardly%20in%20my%20office.%20After%20seeing%20how%20it%20cleans%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20worth%20the%20real%20estate%2C%20but%20keep%20this%20in%20mind%20if%20you%20also%20live%20in%20a%20small%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20images%20showing%20the%20Roborock%20F25%20Ultra%20positioned%20on%20its%20charging%20and%20self-cleaning%20dock.%20The%20left%20image%20shows%20the%20full%20vacuum%20standing%20upright%20on%20a%20hardwood%20floor%20near%20a%20wall%20outlet%2C%20while%20the%20right%20image%20is%20a%20close-up%20of%20the%20dock's%20top%20surface%20with%20visible%20moisture%20and%20the%20Roborock%20logo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f90c0f0be9845f2dc4e357%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20machine%20is%20bigger%20than%20my%20Dyson%20cordless.%20It%20sits%20on%20its%20charging%20station%20when%20not%20in%20use.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f92a7c1-76a2-466b-a41d-b35b3b320757%5C%22%3EAssembly%20was%20intuitive%2C%20which%20is%20good%20because%20the%20instructions%20aren't%20very%20helpful%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAssembly%20involves%20clicking%20the%20handle%2C%20water%20tanks%2C%20and%20roller%20brush%20into%20place.%20I%20initially%20tried%20to%20read%20the%20instructions%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20all%20the%20pieces%20puzzle%20together%2C%20but%20it%20left%20me%20overwhelmed.%20The%20instructions%20feature%20few%20words%20and%20instead%20a%20bunch%20of%20pictures%20and%20numbered%20diagrams.%20I%20decided%20to%20use%20my%20intuition%20to%20get%20the%20mop%20up%20and%20running%2C%20and%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20much%20simpler%20than%20the%20instructions%20let%20on.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20base%20and%20the%20vacuum%20itself%2C%20the%20package%20comes%20with%20a%20spare%20filter%20and%20a%20bottle%20of%20floor%20cleaner.%20Once%20all%20the%20pieces%20were%20in%20place%2C%20I%20simply%20filled%20up%20the%20clean%20water%20tank%20with%20water%20and%20floor%20cleaner%20(the%20vacuum%20automatically%20mixes%20the%20two%20as%20you%20clean)%2C%20charged%20up%20the%20vac%2C%20and%20took%20it%20for%20a%20whirl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d356538-e38b-46c5-b9bf-c79025be0b23%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cleaning%20performance%5C%22%3ECleaning%20performance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20comparison%20of%20a%20white%20tiled%20floor%20before%20and%20after%20cleaning.%20The%20left%20side%20shows%20dirt%2C%20hair%2C%20and%20stains%20on%20the%20tiles%2C%20while%20the%20right%20side%20shows%20the%20same%20area%20spotless%20and%20shiny.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f905fe599d46a4ccc0a310%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221441%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20kitchen%20floor%20before%20(left)%20and%20after%20(right)%20steam%20cleaning%20with%20the%20Roborock%20F25%20Ultra.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20four%20cleaning%20modes%20to%20choose%20from%3A%20sponge%2C%20hot%20water%2C%20steam%2C%20and%20auto.%20Unfortunately%2C%20neither%20the%20manual%20nor%20the%20app%20give%20you%20much%20information%20about%20the%20different%20modes%2C%20but%20from%20what%20I%20can%20glean%20sponge%20mode%20is%20for%20sucking%20up%20liquid%20spills%2C%20auto%20mode%20is%20standard%20non-heated%20cleaning%2C%20hot%20water%20cleans%20at%20187%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20and%20steam%20cleans%20at%20302%20degrees%20Fahrenheit.%20Being%20that%20steam%20was%20the%20element%20that%20sold%20me%20on%20the%20F25%20Ultra%2C%20it%20was%20the%20mode%20I%20chose%20for%20my%20inaugural%20clean%20with%20the%20vac-mop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20baffling%20reasons%2C%20my%20landlord%20decided%20to%20outfit%20our%20apartment%20floors%20with%20bright%20white%20tile.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20I%20see%20every%20single%20speck%20of%20dirt%20or%20minor%20stain%2C%20and%20I%20need%20to%20mop%20my%20floors%20daily%20to%20keep%20them%20presentable.%20Some%20stains%20predate%20my%20tenancy%2C%20and%20I%20just%20assumed%20they%20were%20baked%20into%20the%20floors%20by%20now%2C%20since%20they%20wouldn't%20come%20off%20no%20matter%20how%20hard%20I%20scrubbed.%20I%20was%20shocked%20when%20the%20Roborock%20was%20able%20to%20get%20them%20up%20in%20just%20a%20few%20passes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUp%20came%20the%20duck%20fat%20I%20thought%20was%20permanently%20leached%20into%20my%20tile%20since%20Thanksgiving.%20Out%20came%20the%20turmeric%20stain%20that%20the%20former%20tenants%20left%20as%20a%20parting%20gift.%20Away%20went%20the%20hair%20that%20had%20been%20accumulating%20in%20the%20hallway%20for%20the%20past%20several%20days.%20Gone%20was%20the%20crusted%20hairball%20near%20my%20cat's%20litterbox.%20In%20just%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20my%20floors%20looked%20brighter%20than%20they'd%20ever%20been%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20I%20also%20subjected%20it%20to%20the%20standard%20cleanup%20tests%20we%20put%20all%20wet-dry%20vacs%20through%2C%20including%20picking%20up%20ketchup%2C%20mustard%2C%20cereal%2C%20hair%2C%20coffee%20grounds%2C%20and%20liquids.%20It%20breezed%20through%20all%20of%20the%20fresh%20stain%20tests%2C%20gobbling%20up%20solid%20debris%20and%20sucking%20up%20liquid.%20Day-old%20stains%20took%20a%20few%20more%20passes%2C%20but%20I%20haven't%20encountered%20any%20stains%20the%20machine%20can't%20lift%20just%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Roborock%20F25%20Ultra%20vacuum%20cleaning%20a%20spill%20of%20red%20sauce%20on%20a%20white%20tile%20floor%2C%20with%20steam%20and%20a%20blue%20light%20visible%20around%20the%20cleaning%20head.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f90816599d46a4ccc0a347%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20also%20used%20the%20vac-mop%20to%20pick%20up%20standardized%20spills%20that%20we%20run%20all%20models%20we%20test%20through.%20You%20can%20see%20the%20steam%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20vacuum%20in%20this%20photo.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2228f1816a-ad94-48bf-a504-1c6413505ae5%5C%22%3ESome%20design%20details%20make%20cleaning%20a%20breeze%2C%20but%20edge%20cleaning%20could%20be%20better.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20front-facing%20light%20helps%20illuminate%20dust%2C%20debris%2C%20and%20stains%2C%20making%20it%20easy%20to%20see%20what%20you've%20missed.%20The%20motorized%20wheels%20glide%20smoothly%20across%20floors%2C%20and%20the%20excellent%20turning%20radius%20means%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20do%20a%20full%20kitchen%20dance%20to%20reach%20tricky%20spots.%20The%20cleaner%20can%20also%20tilt%20nearly%20flat%20to%20fit%20under%20most%20furniture.%20An%20onboard%20LED%20screen%20shows%20you%20which%20mode%20you're%20cleaning%20in%20and%20the%20remaining%20battery%20life%20percentage%20as%20you%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Close-up%20of%20the%20Roborock%20F25%20Ultra's%20digital%20display%20showing%20a%20glowing%20purple%20ring%20and%20the%20number%2095%2C%20with%20icons%20for%20Wi-Fi%20and%20cleaning%20mode%20visible%20against%20a%20glossy%20black%20finish.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f9078e599d46a4ccc0a336%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20display%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20vacuum%20shows%20you%20the%20battery%20percentage%20and%20current%20mode%20as%20you%20clean.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20edge%20cleaning%20isn't%20its%20strong%20suit.%20It%20tends%20to%20leave%20faint%20mop%20lines%2C%20especially%20around%20appliances%20where%20the%20cleaning%20head%20can't%20quite%20reach.%20While%20it%20has%20good%20side%20reach%20and%20gets%20close%20to%20walls%2C%20the%20taller%20profile%20of%20the%20cleaning%20head%20limits%20access%20to%20tight%20spaces%2C%20like%20the%20toe%20kicks%20under%20cabinets%20and%20appliances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20my%20cat%20and%20me%2C%20we're%20a%20hairy%20household.%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20to%20see%20that%20the%20copious%20amounts%20of%20hair%20that%20the%20vacuum%20picked%20up%20did%20not%20wrap%20around%20the%20brush%20roll%20or%20clog%20the%20filter.%20Instead%2C%20it%20was%20all%20grossly%20waiting%20for%20me%20in%20the%20strainer%20of%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22397845da-e8a2-4ec1-aeef-d72efe5f671d%5C%22%3ESteam%20mode%20is%20the%20standout%20feature%2C%20but%20it's%20got%20a%20few%20quirks.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20quibble%20I%20have%20with%20the%20steam%20mode%20is%20that%20you%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20steam%20to%20heat%20up%20before%20you%20can%20use%20it.%20That's%20not%20unusual%20for%20any%20steam%20mop%20%E2%80%94%20it%20takes%20time%20for%20water%20to%20heat%20up.%20However%2C%20the%20way%20the%20Roborock%20handles%20it%20essentially%20leaves%20you%20standing%20there%20with%20the%20vacuum%20in%20your%20hand%20for%20a%20minute%2C%20since%20the%20handle%20must%20be%20actively%20engaged%20for%20the%20steam%20mode%20to%20activate.%20A%20count-up%20timer%20on%20the%20display%20ticks%20up%20to%20100%20to%20let%20you%20know%20when%20it's%20ready.%20Or%2C%20if%20you're%20impatient%20like%20me%2C%20you%20can%20just%20start%20cleaning%20while%20it's%20heating%20up%20and%20go%20over%20the%20tough%20spots%20later%20when%20the%20machine%20is%20at%20temp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteam%20mode%20also%20isn't%20for%20wood%20or%20LVP%20floors%20(I%20don't%20think%20I'd%20use%20hot%20water%20mode%20on%20wood%20floors%20either)%2C%20as%20it%20can%20cause%20warping%20and%20cracking.%20I'd%20stick%20with%20auto%20mode%20for%20wood%20flooring%20and%20save%20the%20heated%20cleaning%20modes%20for%20tile%20and%20more%20durable%20flooring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22113b95ad-cda7-4db1-8e4a-38bc0737423c%5C%22%3EIt%20has%20a%20huge%20water%20tank%20and%20solid%20battery%20life.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20water%20tank%20is%20decently%20sized%20at%201%2C000%20milliliters%20plus%20a%20100%20milliliter%20detergent%20tank.%20This%20is%20bigger%20than%20any%20of%20the%20picks%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20best%20wet-dry%20vacuums.%20Functionally%2C%20it%20took%20about%20two%20big%20cleans%20of%20my%20apartment%20before%20I%20was%20prompted%20to%20refill%20the%20tank%20by%20a%20pleasant%20voice%20alert%20from%20the%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20apartment%20is%20just%20550-square%20feet%2C%20so%20a%20single%20charge%20is%20more%20than%20enough%20time%20to%20clean%20the%20entire%20place%20with%20plenty%20of%20battery%20to%20spare.%20Roborock%20claims%20the%20battery%20should%20last%2060%20minutes%20in%20auto%20mode%20and%20about%2015-20%20minutes%20in%20hot%20water%20or%20steam%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221b2eb4a3-6377-40ba-aeaf-3851b755b801%5C%22%3EThe%20app%20is%20worth%20downloading%2C%20but%20not%20essential.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI%20initially%20downloaded%20the%20app%20hoping%20to%20would%20clarify%20some%20information%20about%20the%20various%20cleaning%20modes.%20It%20didn't%2C%20but%20I%20did%20find%20some%20other%20helpful%20settings%20and%20information%20not%20available%20on%20the%20onboard%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20logged%20in%2C%20I%20was%20prompted%20to%20install%20a%20firmware%20update%2C%20which%20was%20a%20nice%20surprise.%20I%20like%20that%20the%20engineering%20team%20continues%20to%20make%20tweaks%20to%20make%20the%20product%20better%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20images%20of%20the%20Roborock%20app.%20The%20left%20image%20shows%20the%20vacuum%20docked%20with%20a%20display%20indicating%20100%25%20charge%20and%20options%20for%20self-cleaning%20and%20drying.%20The%20right%20image%20shows%20the%20vacuum%20in%20use%20with%20an%20interface%20displaying%20cleaning%20modes%20and%20adjustable%20settings%20for%20suction%20force%2C%20water%20level%2C%20and%20drive%20wheels.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f906ccc007ca8c27376ba0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20screenshots%20from%20the%20Roborock%20app%3A%20on%20the%20left%20is%20the%20main%20screen%2C%20showing%20battery%20life%20and%20current%20settings%3B%20on%20the%20right%20shows%20customizations%20you%20can%20make%20for%20each%20cleaning%20mode.%3Cp%3ERoborock%2FLauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20plus%20in%20the%20app%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20customize%20the%20cleaning%20modes.%20You%20can%20adjust%20the%20suction%20level%2C%20water%20level%2C%20detergent%20level%2C%20how%20much%20assist%20the%20adaptive%20wheels%20provide%2C%20and%20whether%20the%20cleaner%20head%20light%20is%20on%20or%20off.%20There%20are%20also%20customizations%20for%20self-cleaning%20and%20heated%20drying%2C%20which%20I'll%20detail%20a%20bit%20more%20below.%20You%20can%20also%20see%20some%20general%20maintenance%20info%20like%20how%20much%20life%20your%20filter%20and%20roller%20have%20until%20it's%20time%20to%20replace%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20wild%20feature%20I%20discovered%20when%20poking%20around%20the%20app%20is%20%26quot%3Bremote%20control%20mode.%26quot%3B%20Essentially%2C%20this%20lets%20you%20lay%20down%20the%20mop%20and%20use%20your%20phone%20to%20drive%20it%20around%20your%20house%20like%20an%20electric%20race%20car.%20I%20wouldn't%20say%20it's%20the%20most%20effective%20way%20to%20clean%20your%20floors%2C%20but%20a%20fun%20option%20with%20some%20boons%20for%20accessibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f874d3d1-6806-440f-90b1-b7ba5a65589e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Care%20and%20maintenance%5C%22%3ECare%20and%20maintenance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Roborock%20F25%20Ultra%20sitting%20on%20its%20base%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f90c83599d46a4ccc0a3dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20charging%20base%20elevates%20the%20brush%20roll%20and%20engages%20brush%20roll%20cleaning%20and%20drying.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22677da7ca-f6bc-410f-a56a-945336811815%5C%22%3ESelf-cleaning%20and%20brush%20roll%20drying%20mean%20minimal%20work%20for%20you.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you're%20done%20cleaning%2C%20the%20vac-mop%20goes%20back%20on%20the%20base%20and%20a%20voice%20prompts%20you%20to%20activate%20the%20self-cleaning%20mode.%20Here%20there%20are%20several%20options%20to%20choose%20from%2C%20like%20heated%20self-clean%2C%20steam%20self-clean%2C%20fast%20drying%2C%20and%20quiet%20drying.%20You%20can%20select%20and%20start%20self-cleaning%20from%20a%20button%20on%20the%20front%20of%20the%20machine%20or%20fully%20customize%20your%20options%20in%20the%20app.%20Some%20app%20options%20include%20scheduling%20self-cleaning%2C%20setting%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20clean%2C%20and%20choosing%20whether%20drying%20starts%20automatically%20after%20self-cleaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vac%20defaults%20to%20heated%20self-cleaning%20with%20quiet%20drying.%20I%20found%20it%20kind%20of%20funny%20that%20a%20voice%20narrates%20each%20step%20of%20the%20minutes-long%20self-cleaning%20process.%20You%20can%20turn%20this%20option%20off%20in%20the%20app%2C%20fortunately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228658dc54-0660-416b-84f2-3f327799ce57%5C%22%3EEmptying%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%20is%20grossly%20satisfying.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it's%20done%20self-cleaning%2C%20you'll%20be%20prompted%20to%20clear%20out%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%20while%20the%20brush%20roll%20undergoes%20heated%20drying.%20I%20don't%20think%20there's%20any%20way%20to%20make%20this%20process%20less%20gross%2C%20but%20basically%20you%20detach%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%2C%20lift%20to%20separate%20the%20solids%20from%20the%20liquids%20and%20dump%20the%20former%20in%20the%20trash%20and%20the%20latter%20in%20the%20sink.%20After%20a%20quick%20rinse%2C%20the%20tank%20is%20ready%20to%20go%20back%20into%20the%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20images%20showing%20the%20aftermath%20of%20cleaning%20with%20the%20Roborock%20F25%20Ultra.%20The%20left%20image%20shows%20a%20hand%20holding%20the%20vacuum's%20dirty%20water%20tank%20filled%20with%20murky%20water%20and%20debris.%20The%20right%20image%20shows%20the%20vacuum's%20brush%20housing%20clogged%20with%20hair%20and%20small%20bits%20of%20dirt%20and%20food.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f908c9c007ca8c27376bd4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20dirty%20water%20tank%20pops%20out%20of%20the%20front%20of%20the%20machine.%20You%20lift%20the%20top%20to%20reveal%20the%20solids%20and%20pour%20out%20the%20liquids%20from%20the%20base.%20As%20you%20can%20see%20here%2C%20the%20vacuum%20picked%20up%20a%20ton%20of%20hair.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20like%20that%20the%20machine%20automates%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20care%20and%20maintenance%20for%20you.%20The%20only%20routine%20hands-on%20task%20is%20emptying%20the%20dirty%20tank%20and%20refilling%20the%20clean%20tanks.%20My%20apartment%20is%20small%2C%20so%20it%20took%20about%20a%20dozen%20uses%20before%20I%20needed%20to%20refill%20the%20water%20and%20cleaning%20solution%20in%20the%20clean%20tank.%20You%20should%20also%20change%20the%20filter%20every%20three%20to%20six%20months.%20The%20machine%20comes%20with%20two%20(one%20installed%2C%20and%20one%20replacement)%20to%20get%20