ider.com%2Fgold-bitcoin-silver-price-debasement-trade-inflation-currency-dollar-dominance-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edebasement%20trade%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20way%20to%20hedge%20against%20a%20falling%20US%20dollar%20amid%20fears%20over%20relentless%20government%20spending%2C%20mounting%20debt%2C%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20another%20bout%20of%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20much%20in%20the%20fundamental%20outlook%20for%20gold%20has%20changed%2C%20save%20for%20perhaps%20a%20small%20rebound%20in%20the%20dollar%2C%20said%20Peter%20Perkins%2C%20a%20global%20strategy%20partner%20at%20MRB%20Partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20pullback%20is%20more%20likely%20due%20to%20extended%20technicals%20after%20the%20roaring%20run-up%2C%20Perkins%20said.%20In%20a%20client%20note%20published%20Tuesday%2C%20Perkins%20pointed%20out%20that%20his%20firm's%20momentum%20indicator%20on%20gold%20had%20drifted%20three%20standard%20deviations%20from%20the%20norm%20going%20back%20to%201985.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221244%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22gold%20rally%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f914bb0be9845f2dc4e4f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221386%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMRB%20Partners%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20a%20momentum%20trade%20that%20got%20overdone%2C%20that's%20really%20all%20it%20looks%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20Perkins%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSomebody%20decided%2C%20'I'm%20gonna%20sell%2C'%20or%20whatever%20the%20case%20may%20be%2C%20and%20it%20just%20triggered%20profit%20taking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGold%2C%20traditionally%20viewed%20as%20a%20safe-haven%20asset%2C%20has%20achieved%20%26quot%3Bmeme-stock%26quot%3B%20status%20this%20year%2C%20PIMCO%20cofounder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbond-king-bill-gross-gold-record-price-meme-stock-outlook-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBill%20Gross%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Business%20Insider%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Tigay%2C%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Eportfolio%20manager%20of%20the%20Rational%20Equity%20Armor%20Fund%2C%20detailed%20in%20an%20email%20some%20of%20the%20mania%20around%20gold%20right%20now%2C%20warning%20of%20a%20bubble%20in%20the%20precious%20metal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20bullish%20on%20gold%20for%20years.%20But%20what%20I'm%20seeing%20now%20keeps%20me%20up%20at%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BHere's%20what%20concerns%20me%3A%20everyone%20talks%20about%20how%20risky%20stocks%20are%2C%20how%20we're%20in%20a%20bubble.%20But%20gold%3F%20Gold%20has%20become%20the%20'risk-free'%20trade.%20Nobody%20questions%20whether%20it's%20lofty.%20That's%20precisely%20when%20you%20should%20question%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETigay%20added%20that%20the%20buying%20of%20physical%20gold%20has%20reached%20frenzied%20levels%2C%20citing%20anecdotes%20of%20lines%20around%20the%20block%20at%20midday%20at%20a%20prominent%20gold%20dealer%20in%20Sydney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20line%20up%20in%20the%20streets%20to%20buy%20an%20asset%2C%20when%20the%20narrative%20becomes%20one-sided%2C%20when%20the%20trade%20gets%20this%20crowded%E2%80%94that's%20your%20signal.%20I%20don't%20care%20what%20the%20asset%20is.%20This%20is%20how%20manias%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20recent%20bump%2C%20some%20think%20the%20rally%20can%20continue.%20Ulrike%20Hoffmann-Burchardi%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20Americas%20and%20global%20head%20of%20equities%20at%20UBS%20Global%20Wealth%20Management%2C%20said%20in%20a%20note%20Wednesday%20that%20political%20uncertainty%2C%20high%20government%20debt%20levels%2C%20and%20central%20bank%20purchases%20should%20continue%20to%20drive%20prices%20higher%20to%20%244%2C700%2C%20representing%20another%2015%25%20upside%20from%20current%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEither%20way%2C%20the%20extreme%20n