ble%20staircase%20decorated%20with%20flowers%2C%20chandeliers%2C%20and%20brass%20handrails%20takes%20visitors%20from%20the%20street%20into%20the%20hotel%20lobby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20hotel%20features%20nods%20to%20romance%20in%20its%20decorations.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22romeo%20and%20juliet%20palmer%20house%20chicago%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f6a3a85dbc4fd10dab2efa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20top%20of%20the%20marble%20staircases%2C%20there's%20a%20bronze%20statue%20of%20Romeo%20and%20Juliet.%20While%20this%20is%20perhaps%20the%20most%20explicit%20nod%20to%20romance%20in%20the%20lobby's%20decorations%2C%20it%20is%20far%20from%20the%20only%20one%20in%20the%20hotel%2C%20which%20was%20a%20symbol%20of%20love%20itself%20as%20a%20wedding%20gift%20from%20Potter%20to%20Bertha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20symbols%20include%20peacocks%20at%20the%20entrance%20and%20figures%20of%20Greek%20mythological%20characters%2C%20like%20the%20Goddess%20of%20Love%2C%20Aphrodite%2C%20in%20the%20lobby's%20ceiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20hotel's%20highlight%20is%20its%20grand%20preserved%20lobby.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222133%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22inside%20chicago%20lockwood%20palmer%20house%20hotel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f796221c1f80efbec5f419%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hotel's%20pride%20and%20joy%20is%20its%20grand%20lobby%2C%20which%20was%20imagined%20as%20a%20type%20of%20European%20drawing%20room%20and%20features%20the%20most%20luxurious%20and%20glamorous%20displays%20of%20the%20original%20owners'%20Gilded%20Age%20taste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ceiling%20features%2021%20panels%20of%20painted%20frescoes%20depicting%20different%20scenes%20from%20Greek%20mythology.%20Once%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.palmerhousehiltonhotel.com%2Fabout-our-hotel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edescribed%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20wonderful%20protest%20of%20romance%20against%20the%20everydayness%20of%20life%26quot%3B%20by%20columnist%20George%20Will%2C%20it%20was%20painted%20by%20the%20French%20artist%20Louis%20Pierre%20Regal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lobby%20was%20inspired%20by%20Bertha%20Palmer's%20friendship%20with%20French%20Impressionist%20painter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclimate-activists-monet-haystacks-painting-mashed-potatoes-environment-germany-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%20Monet%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBertha%20Palmer%2C%20who%20was%20dedicated%20to%20decorating%20the%20Palmer%20House%20with%20French%20art%20as%20a%20nod%20to%20her%20family's%20heritage%2C%20is%20said%20to%20have%20accumulated%20the%20largest%20collection%20of%20Impressionist%20art%20outside%20of%20France%2C%20most%20of%20it%20now%20living%20inside%20the%20Art%20Institute%20of%20Chicago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnother%20marble%20staircase%20leads%20from%20the%20lobby%20to%20the%20Empire%20Room.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22empre%20room%20palmer%20house%20lockwood%20chicago%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c8803b57d362d375e83420%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20marble%20staircase%20features%20two%2024-karat%20gold-dipped%20bronze%20statues%20and%20candelabras%20designed%20by%20Louis%20Comfort%20Tiffany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20the%20two%20Winged%20Angels%20weighs%201.25%20tons%20and%20are%20said%20to%20be%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20structures%20designed%20by%20Tiffany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lobby%20also%20features%20Tiffany%20chandeliers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Empire%20Room%20once%20hosted%20performers%20like%20Frank%20Sinatra%2C%20Judy%20Garland%2C%20and%20Ella%20Fitzgerald.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224437%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22empire%20ballroom%20palmer%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f796c9cc993f9955d09074%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223328%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Hiltons%20of%20Chicago%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAtop%20the%20marble%20staircases%20is%20the%20Empire%20Room%2C%20which%20was%20once%20the%20hotel's%20main%20dining%20room%20and%20main%20stage%20for%20the%20big-name%20musicians%20who%20came%20to%20perform%20at%20the%20Palmer%20House's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupper-clubs-gen-z-ditching-drinking-bars-restaurants-socializing-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esupper%20club%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20club%20served%20as%20a%20major%20entertainment%20hub%20in%20the%20city%2C%20operating%20from%201932%20to%201976.%20It%20welcomed%20stars%20like%20Frank%20Sinatra%2C%20Judy%20Garland%2C%20Ella%20Fitzgerald%2C%20Harry%20Belafonte%2C%20and%20Louis%20Armstrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20it%20has%20been%20used%20as%20a%20venue%20for%20private%20events%20such%20as%20weddings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20lobby's%20mezzanine%20gives%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20painted%20ceiling.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224437%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22palmer%20house%20mezzanine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f79648cc993f9955d0905f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223328%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Hiltons%20of%20Chicago%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20mezzanine%20with%20balconies%20overlooks%20the%20lobby.%20It%20almost%20begs%