because%20they%20grow%20easily%20in%20our%20soil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20emphasises%20that%20the%20approach%20to%20millets%20matters%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20introduce%20them%20in%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20first%20foods%2C%20say%2C%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eporridge%20at%20seven%20months%2C%20they%20accept%20it%20as%20normal.%20But%20if%20you%20suddenly%20swap%20rice%20for%20jowar%20at%20age%20five%2C%20there%20will%20be%20resistance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20recommend%20to%20clients%20is%20that%20for%20the%20first%20two%20to%20three%20weeks%2C%20you%20start%20with%20just%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20to%20let%20your%20child%20ease%20into%20solids.%20Around%20six%20and%20a%20half%20months%2C%20you%20can%20introduce%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343315%2Fbiggest-millet-exporters-in-india-ra-foods-sisters-priya-akila-gunasekar-run-multi-crore-millet-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrains%20like%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20jowar%2C%20quinoa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20rice%2C%20since%20they%20need%20the%20carbs.%20To%20make%20these%20easier%20to%20digest%2C%20you%20can%20soak%20them%20overnight%20in%20warm%20water%20or%20even%20with%20a%20little%20lemon%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20also%20notes%20that%20millets%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20feel%20%E2%80%9Cboring%E2%80%9D%20or%20traditional.%20%E2%80%9CParents%20can%20make%20millet%20waffles%2C%20millet%20pizza%20bases%2C%20or%20even%20millet-based%20cookies.%20Kids%20respond%20better%20when%20the%20food%20looks%20familiar%20but%20is%20nutritionally%20upgraded.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2F